going to be safe."

40:26.493 --> 40:28.011
And then in came
the gentrification,

40:28.046 --> 40:29.979
and so the whole concept of
America is being wiped out,

40:30.013 --> 40:32.257
because you can't pull yourself
up by the bootstraps anymore

40:32.291 --> 40:33.983
'cause you can't
get in the game.

40:34.017 --> 40:35.812
[soft music]

40:35.847 --> 40:37.987
Gentrification has affected
the whole city.

40:38.021 --> 40:41.715
You have to now make a huge
amount of money to be here.

40:41.749 --> 40:43.820
