40:54.762 --> 40:57.144
- Yes. New York,
there was always something

40:57.178 --> 40:58.697
that brought it back,

40:58.732 --> 41:01.148
but once you fill it
with the corporate world,

41:01.182 --> 41:02.874
it's never going back.

41:02.908 --> 41:06.118
